 MBOMBELA – Local individuals and businesses decorated the chairs, all in varying ways and with different stories behind them. Eighty-five chairs are going under the hammer. The online auction in aid of Nelspruit Hospice runs until September 4. To participate, click here. To get a closer look at all the chairs up for auction visit i’langa Mall where the chairs are being displayed. Visit Nelspruit Hospice‘s Facebook page to read some of the beautiful stories behind the inspiration for the art. For more information contact Nelspruit Hospice on 013-744-0095 or 079-070-2166. READ MORE: Nelspruit Hospice one of the most caring organisations